runs what he calls the Shamanic

00:32:03.910 --> 00:32:08.795 align:middle line:84%
Cabaret, where it's the six-hour
show of Joseph Campbell's hero

00:32:08.795 --> 00:32:09.595 align:middle line:90%
journey.

00:32:09.595 --> 00:32:10.405 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Six hours?

